<br />
<br />About the vibrato stuff, it's definitely something subjective and depending on style (would suck if everyone's music sounded the same, right?).  I mostly just wanted to point out that the Dragon Warrior series had some of my favorite NES music, and I think only 2 songs in the whole series had used vibrato (both on the triangle channel).

		

